I'm sorry, I do not have access to real-time information on the current top Colombian food trucks in the US. However, here is a list of some popular Colombian food trucks that have gained recognition in various cities:

1. La Cocinita - Miami, FL
2. Que Chevere - New York, NY
3. La Cevicheria - Los Angeles, CA
4. Comida - Austin, TX
5. Tostones - Chicago, IL
6. El Guapo - Denver, CO
7. Que Bacano - Washington, D.C.
8. Empanada Top - San Francisco, CA
9. Las Chicas - Houston, TX
10. El Caribefunk - Seattle, WA

Please note that this list is not exhaustive and there may be other popular Colombian food trucks in different parts of the country.
